FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about using our app to find promising cryptocurrency investments.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What types of cryptocurrencies can I find on your app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app surfaces a wide range of new and emerging cryptocurrencies across different sectors like DeFi, NFTs, gaming, and more. We prioritize showcasing innovative projects with strong fundamentals.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How are new cryptocurrencies evaluated and selected?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Our team of crypto experts thoroughly researches and vets each project based on criteria like the core technology, team credentials, tokenomics, and real-world utility. Only high-potential cryptos make the cut.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What information is provided about each cryptocurrency?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: You'll find detailed overviews covering the project concept, roadmap, key metrics, and more. We also analyze factors like market cap, trading volume, and community engagement.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is there a way to track my favorite upcoming cryptos?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! You can build a personalized watchlist of cryptocurrencies that interest you most. We'll notify you about major updates and when they get listed on exchanges.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How can I start using the app to find new crypto gems?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Just download our app and create an account! You'll gain full access to browse and research all the exciting crypto projects we cover. Don't miss out on the next big cryptocurrency!
